## Rust Crate Dependencies (linked, not vendored)

The following Rust crates are used as dependencies and linked into the
native libraries. They are resolved by Cargo at build time and are NOT
included in this repository.

  libc 0.2           — MIT OR Apache-2.0
  freetype 0.7       — MIT (optional: sge-freetype crate)
  freetype-sys        — MIT (optional: sge-freetype crate)
  rapier2d 0.22      — Apache-2.0 (optional: sge-physics crate)
  rapier3d 0.22      — Apache-2.0 (optional: sge-physics3d crate)
  image 0.25         — MIT OR Apache-2.0 (optional: android feature)

For the complete list, see native-components/Cargo.toml.
